Package: SfSpHelpers
Type: Package
Title: Some functions to deal with sf/sp objects
Version: 0.4.1
Author: Charles Gauvin
Maintainer: Charles Gauvin <charles.gauvin123@gmail.com>
Description: Basic utility functions such as adding centroids without changing the geometry, download zipped shp files, 
    getting 2D KDE density polygons for plotting, removing a fixed proportion from linestring endpoints, voronoi-based spatial interpolation, etc.
